位於[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]（印尼）[[雅加達|雅加達]]中區基艾·哈吉·瓦希德·哈希姆路（Jalan Kyai Haji Wahid Hasyim）和[[M·H·譚林路|M·H·譚林路]]交界處的{{en-link|莎麗娜百貨|Sarinah}}附近在2016年1月14日發生多宗爆炸案和槍擊案<ref name="reuters">{{cite news |title=Blasts, gunfight in Indonesian capital; at least three dead |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-blast-idUSKCN0US0BS20160114 |agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |accessdate=14 January 2016 |archive-date=2016-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114102918/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-blast-idUSKCN0US0BS20160114 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中一枚炸彈在一家[[星巴克|星巴克]]咖啡店爆炸，另一枚則在莎麗娜百貨外的一個警崗爆炸<ref name="reuters" />。事發地點鄰近[[聯合國|聯合國]]資訊中心、數家豪華酒店和數家{{Link-en|駐印度尼西亞外交機構列表|List of diplomatic missions in Indonesia|外國駐印尼使領館}}（包括{{Link-fr|法國駐印度尼西亞大使館|Ambassade de France en Indonésie|法國大使館}}）<ref name="bbc">{{cite news|title=Jakarta attacks: Bombs and gunfire rock Indonesian capital|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35309195|website=BBC News|publisher=BBC|accessdate=14 January 2016|archive-date=2019-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505100151/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35309195|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[聯合國環境署|聯合國環境署]]證實，一名荷蘭籍聯合國工作人員在襲擊中重傷<ref name="bbc2" />。至當日12時，M·H·譚林路扎克拉瓦拉大廈（Gedung Cakrawala）4樓也發生警方與武裝份子對峙的局面<ref>{{Cite web|title = Kapolda dan Kapolres Jakpus Masuk ke Gedung Cakrawala Meski Ada Baku Tembak|url = http://news.detik.com/berita/3118334/kapolda-dan-kapolres-jakpus-masuk-ke-gedung-cakrawala-meski-ada-baku-tembak|website = detiknews|access-date = 2016-01-14|language = id|archive-date = 2016-01-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117124641/http://news.detik.com/berita/3118334/kapolda-dan-kapolres-jakpus-masuk-ke-gedung-cakrawala-meski-ada-baku-tembak|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在這次襲擊中，至少有8人身亡，當中包括4名襲擊者和4位平民（3個印尼人和一個加拿大人），另外還有23人受傷。[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]已經就這次襲擊承認責任<ref name=bbc2>{{cite news|authors=Penny Spiller, Claudia Allen, Alastair Lawson, Tessa Wong, Saira Asher, Heather Chen, Simeon Paterson & Naziru Mikailu|title=As it happened: Jakarta attacks|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/live/world-asia-35309116|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=BBC News|date=14 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114064137/http://www.bbc.com/news/live/world-asia-35309116|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
雖然印尼和中東的衝突相隔甚遠，不過該國在過去20年已經經歷過幾次由伊斯蘭教武裝份子發動，令數百人喪生的恐怖襲擊<ref name=nyt />。

這是[[2009年雅加達酒店爆炸案|2009年雅加達酒店爆炸案]]以來雅加達遭到的第一次大規模襲擊事件。2009年的爆炸案由[[伊斯蘭祈禱團|伊斯蘭祈禱團]]發動，引致7人和另外兩名襲擊者死亡<ref name=nyt />。伊斯蘭祈禱團是一個與[[基地組織|基地組織]]有聯繫的組織，尋求以[[伊斯蘭國_(政權形式)|伊斯蘭國]]的形式統一印尼、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]和[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]南部<ref name="cfr">{{cite web |title=Terrorism Havens: Indonesia |publisher=Council on Foreign Relations |date=December 2005 |url=http://www.cfr.org/publication/9361/ |accessdate=17 July 2009 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5iccilBBM?url=http://www.cfr.org/publication/9361/ |archivedate=2009-07-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=NYTMilitants>{{cite news|title=Militants Eyed in Indonesian Bombings|first=Norimitsu|last=Onishi|date=17 July 2009|accessdate=18 July 2009|publisher=''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/18/world/asia/18indo.html|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115075946/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/18/world/asia/18indo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自[[2002年峇里島爆炸案|2002年峇里島爆炸案]]令超過200人喪生以來，印尼當局就開始加緊鎮壓恐怖主義。印尼的立法機構在2003年通過一份反恐怖主義條例<ref>{{cite book |editor= Ramraj, Hor, & Roach |title= Global Anti-Terrorism Law and Policy |url= https://archive.org/details/globalantiterror00ramr |year= 2005 |publisher= Cambridge University Press |isbn= 0-521-85125-4 |page= [https://archive.org/details/globalantiterror00ramr/page/295 295] }}</ref>。

印尼國家警察發言人表示，警方在2015年11月就已經接獲訊息，得知伊斯蘭國警告印尼將發生襲擊事件<ref name=nyt />。總部位於雅加達的衝突政策分析研究院（Institute for Policy Analysis of Conflict）在2015年的報導中指出，和數以千計的外國戰士一起到敘利亞加入協助極端主義組織試圖在當地成立伊斯蘭國的行列的印尼人至少有50人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cochrane|first1=Joe|title=Indonesian Militants Join Foreigners Fighting in Syria|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/01/world/asia/indonesian-militants-join-fight-in-syria.html|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=The New York Times|date=31 January 2014|archive-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719023629/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/01/world/asia/indonesian-militants-join-fight-in-syria.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 襲擊 ==
[[File:2016_Sarinah-Starbucks_Jakarta_Attack_7.JPG|thumb]]
據報導，[[雅加達中區|雅加達中區]]在2016年1月14日當地時間早上10時40分發生幾次爆炸，並在隨後發生槍擊案。事發地點是很多豪華酒店、辦公大樓和大使館的所在地<ref name=dawn />。印尼國家警察發言人表示，這次襲擊涉及到配備手榴彈和槍械，為數不明的襲擊者<ref name=nyt/>。新聞傳媒統計雅加達合共發生了七次爆炸，死者多達6人，當中包括3名警員。報導也指出有10至14名襲擊者參與這次事件<ref name=guardian>{{cite news|last1=Safi|first1=Michael|last2=Weaver|first2=Matthew|title=Jakarta attacks: at least six dead in series of 'suicide bombings' – live updates|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jan/14/multiple-explosions-gunshots-reported-in-jakarta-rolling-report|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=the Guardian|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114050257/http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jan/14/multiple-explosions-gunshots-reported-in-jakarta-rolling-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

襲擊的目標是一個位於主要路口，鄰近[[星巴克|星巴克]]咖啡店和[[漢堡王|漢堡王]]分店的交通警崗，炸彈爆炸令該警崗嚴重損毀<ref name=nyt>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/15/world/asia/jakarta-explosion.html?_r=0|title=Jakarta Attack Kills at Least 2, Indonesian Officials Say|last=Cochrane|first=Joe|date=2016-01-14|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2016-01-14|location=Jakarta|archive-date=2016-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116042335/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/15/world/asia/jakarta-explosion.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有傳聞指出芝基尼（Cikini）、斯利比（Slipi）和古寧安（Kuningan）村區土耳其和巴基斯坦大使館附近也有三起炸彈爆炸<ref>{{cite news|title=The Latest: 3 More Blasts Near Turkish, Pakistan Embassies|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/latest-explosions-reported-jakarta-36279316|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=ABC News|archive-date=2016-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116220435/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/latest-explosions-reported-jakarta-36279316|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過雅加達警方既否認了這些傳聞，也否認西馬杜邦（Simatupang）和巴美拉（Palmerah）發生襲擊案，並表示這些事情都只是惡作劇<ref>{{cite news |title=Jakarta attacks: seven dead in multiple attacks linked to Islamic State |url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/explosion-near-sarinah-a-shopping-mall-in-central-jakarta-20160114-gm5uvl.html |work=Sydney Morning Herald |date=14 January 2016 |author=Jewel Topsfield |accessdate=14 January 2016 |archive-date=2016-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116172947/http://www.smh.com.au/world/explosion-near-sarinah-a-shopping-mall-in-central-jakarta-20160114-gm5uvl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。位於聯合國辦事處附近的莎麗娜百貨前方發生了一次爆炸。<ref name=dawn>{{cite news|title=7 dead as series of blasts rock Indonesian capital|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1232909/7-dead-as-series-of-blasts-rock-indonesian-capital|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=www.dawn.com|date=14 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115032247/http://www.dawn.com/news/1232909/7-dead-as-series-of-blasts-rock-indonesian-capital|dead-url=no}}</ref>

事後發放的片段據稱顯示了兩個襲擊者在星巴克分店外一顆炸彈爆炸的時候擠作一團，然後被炸死的情形<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mills|first1=Kelly-Ann|title=Chilling new footage shows moment ISIS thugs detonate suicide bomb during Jakarta attack|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/chilling-new-footage-shows-moment-7185469|work=The Daily Mirror|accessdate=16 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117093424/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/chilling-new-footage-shows-moment-7185469|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Webb|first1=Sam|title=Jakarta terror attack: ISIS suicide bombers captured detonating explosive vest outside Starbucks in horrific footage|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/jakarta-terror-attack-isis-suicide-7178508|accessdate=16 January 2016|work=The Daily Mirror|archive-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117070945/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/jakarta-terror-attack-isis-suicide-7178508|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一組圖片顯示兩個槍手向在M·H·譚林路被炸彈炸毀的警崗周圍聚集的群眾開槍。第一個槍手似乎是向兩名警員開槍，之後群眾便退散。而第二個槍手則近距離射擊另一名警員。警方發言人表示第一個槍手在扎克拉瓦拉大廈停車場挾持兩名人質，卻在其後和另一個槍手雙雙被警方射殺<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mononimbar|first1=Donny Andhika|last2=Karensa|first2=Edo|last3=Almanar|first3=Alin|last4=Arnaz|first4=Farouk|title=Police Say Five Terrorists Killed in Jakarta Attacksi|url=http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/news/police-say-five-terrorists-killed-jakarta-attacks/|work=Jakarta Globe|accessdate=16 January 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115173049/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/news/police-say-five-terrorists-killed-jakarta-attacks/|archivedate=2016年1月15日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Yudhi|title=Tempo Photojournalist Captures Moments When Two Terrorists Go on a Shooting Rampage|url=http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/eyewitness/tempo-photo-journalist-captures-moments-two-terrorist-suspects-shot-police-thamrin-road/|work=Jakarta Globe|accessdate=16 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117184300/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/eyewitness/tempo-photo-journalist-captures-moments-two-terrorist-suspects-shot-police-thamrin-road/|archive-date=2016-01-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 襲擊者 ==
雅加達警方表示，一個名為巴赫鲁姆·纳伊姆（Bahrun Naim），與伊斯蘭國有聯繫的印尼極端份子是這次襲擊的幕後主腦。被認為是[[中爪哇省|中爪哇省]][[北加浪岸|北加浪岸]]人的纳伊姆在襲擊發生前的某個時候轉往敘利亞[[拉卡|拉卡]]；印尼警方至少從2010年開始得知此人的身分<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-01-14/jakarta-bombing-suspected-terrorists-civilians-dead-after-attack/7089218 Jakarta bombing: Attackers, civilians killed in blasts claimed by Islamic State, police say] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-01-14/jakarta-bombing-suspected-terrorists-civilians-dead-after-attack/7089218 |date=20160115043945 }}, [[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]] (January 14, 2016).</ref><ref name="BBCProfileNaim">[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35316915 Jakarta attacks: Profile of suspect Bahrun Naim] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35316915 |date=20160116122448 }}, BBC News (January 14, 2016).</ref>。纳伊姆曾出面維護一個網誌，他在網誌中讚揚包括[[2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件|2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件]]在內的恐怖襲擊，並呼籲印尼人在印尼群島發動同類的襲擊<ref name="BBCProfileNaim"/><ref>Joe Cochrane, [http://www.nytimes.com/live/jakarta-indonesia-explosions/ Bahrun Naim, Suspect in Jakarta Attack, Appears to Have Praised Paris Assaults in Blog] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/jakarta-indonesia-explosions/ |date=20160114194956 }}, ''New York Times'' (January 14, 2016).</ref>。纳伊姆曾在2010年11月在位於[[梭羅市|梭羅市]]的寓所被當局以涉嫌與恐怖組織有聯繫為由逮捕，並於翌年6月以藏有武器的罪名被定罪，然而法庭卻由於證據不足而無法裁定其涉及恐怖主義的罪名成立<ref name="BBCProfileNaim"/>。

警方能夠辨認出其中一名襲擊者，他叫做阿菲夫·蘇納金（Afif Sunakim），他在發動襲擊期間被發現攜帶槍械，背着帆布背包。他曾經因為在武裝份子訓練營受訓而被判監7年<ref name=BBCNews>{{cite news|title=Jakarta attacks: Convicted militant named as attacker|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35320352|accessdate=15 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115144946/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35320352|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在自殺式炸彈襲擊中被炸死的兩名襲擊者已被確認為Dian Juni Kurniadi和Ahmad Muhazab Saron<ref name=deadidentities>{{cite web|last1=Arnaz|first1=Farouk|title=Five Attackers or Four? Police Still Unsure|url=http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/news/five-attackers-four-police-still-unsure/|publisher=Jakarta Globe|accessdate=16 January 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117192328/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/news/five-attackers-four-police-still-unsure/|archivedate=2016年1月17日}}</ref>。在和警方駁火期間被擊斃的襲擊者是阿菲夫（又稱蘇納金、蘇納迪）和馬爾萬（又稱莫哈末阿里）<ref name=deadidentities/>。

