== 各方反應 ==
=== 印尼國內 ===
[[File:2016_Sarinah-Starbucks_Jakarta_Attack_5.JPG|thumb]]
印尼總統[[佐科·維多多|佐科·維多多]]藉着電視轉播發表聲明，把這次襲擊稱為「恐怖行為」。在他的聲明中，佐科表示：「我们的国家和国民不應該害怕，我们不会被这些恐怖行为打败。我希望公众保持冷静。我們都為這次事件中的死者感到悲傷，不過我們也譴責這次行動破壞和平安全，並在民眾之間散播恐怖。<ref name=nyt2>{{cite news|last1=Cochrane|first1=Joe|title=Four Confirmed Dead in Jakarta|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/jakarta-indonesia-explosions/four-confirmed-dead-in-jakarta/|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=The New York Times - The New York Times|date=14 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116050735/http://www.nytimes.com/live/jakarta-indonesia-explosions/four-confirmed-dead-in-jakarta/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」

雅加達和印尼各地居民都都在社交網站轉載他的聲明「我們不害怕」，並以[[主題標籤|主題標籤]]#kamitidaktakut標示這個話題。這個主題標籤得到Twitter用戶的廣泛使用，他們會藉着這個標籤向死難者致哀和蔑視這次襲擊<ref name=bbc2 />。

星巴克也發表了一份新聞公告，譴責襲擊事件<ref name=bbc2 />，並表示將關閉其所有位於雅加達的分店，「直至另行通知」<ref>{{cite news|title=Starbucks closing Jakarta stores 'until further notice': Statement|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/business/starbucks-closing-jakarta/2425332.html|accessdate=14 January 2016|work=[[Channel_NewsAsia|Channel NewsAsia]]|agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]|publisher=MediaCorp|date=14 January 2016|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114100732/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/business/starbucks-closing-jakarta/2425332.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

印尼國家警察一名警員在事發後一天表示警方在調查14日在首都發生，為期4小時，引致7人死亡的襲擊事件的過程當中已拘留三人<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/indonesian-police-say-they-ve-arrested-three-jakarta-attacks-n496966 | title = Indonesian Police Say Three Detained After Jakarta Attacks | publisher = NBC News | accessdate = 15 January 2016 | archive-date = 2016-01-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160115055352/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/indonesian-police-say-they-ve-arrested-three-jakarta-attacks-n496966 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，事發兩天後，警方又拘捕了12個人，他們被指控涉嫌策劃針對印尼政府、警方和外國人命財產的襲擊，並與在襲擊中被射殺的攻擊者保持聯繫<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title = Indonesian police arrest 12 over Jakarta attack|url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-01-16/indonesian-police-arrest-12-over-jakarta-attack/7093458|website = ABC News|access-date = 2016-01-16|archive-date = 2016-01-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117024421/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-01-16/indonesian-police-arrest-12-over-jakarta-attack/7093458|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

